&lt;td style="border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid 0.75pt black; border-right: solid 0.75pt black; padding: 0pt"&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-right: 9.0pt; text-align: right; line-height: 10.0pt"&gt;
88&lt;/p&gt;
